  "steps": [
    "Heat a shallow non-stick pan, add dried red chillies, coriander seeds, peppercorns and fenugreek seeds, mix and dry roast for 2-3 minutes. Allow to cool.",
    "Transfer the roasted ingredients into a grinder jar, add coconut, roughly chopped onion, tamarind, turmeric powder and ¾ cup water and grind to fine paste.",
    "Heat ghee in a non-stick kadai, add mustard seeds and once they start to splutter, add asafoetida and curry leaves, mix and sauté for a few seconds.",
    "Add chopped onion, salt and green chillies, mix and sauté till onion turns translucent. Add sprouted green gram, mix and sauté for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add 2 cups water, cover and cook for 5-6 minutes. Add ground paste and tirphal and mix well. Cover and cook on medium heat for 8-10 minutes.",
    "Add jaggery and coriander leaves, mix and cook till jaggery dissolves.",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl, garnish with coriander sprig and serve hot with steamed rice."
  ],
